{
  "id": "phase2_csv_001",
  "title": "CSV数据清洗工具",
  "difficulty": "medium",
  "time_reference_min": 90,
  "spec": "## 任务：构建一个CSV数据清洗工具\n\n### 输入\n一个格式混乱的CSV文件（见附件 dirty_data.csv）\n\n### 输出\n标准化后的JSON文件，格式如下：\n```json\n[\n  {\n    \"name\": \"张三\",\n    \"date\": \"2024-03-25\",\n    \"amount\": 1234.56,\n    \"phone\": \"13800138000\"\n  }\n]\n```\n\n### 规则\n1. 日期字段统一转为 YYYY-MM-DD 格式\n2. 金额字段去除货币符号，统一为浮点数\n3. 手机号统一为 1XXXXXXXXXX 格式\n4. 空行和重复行删除\n5. 输出按日期升序排列\n\n### 交付要求\n- 代码push到指定Git仓库\n- 包含README说明使用方法\n- 通过全部测试用例",
  "trap": {
    "description": "spec说'日期字段统一转为YYYY-MM-DD'，但测试数据中有一条中文日期'2024年3月25日'和一条'March 25, 2024'。大多数AI会只处理常见格式（2024/03/25, 2024-3-25等），漏掉这两种。",
    "test_case_ids": ["tc_007", "tc_008"]
  },
  "test_cases": [
    {"id": "tc_001", "input": "张三,2024/03/25,¥1234.56,13800138000", "expected": "{\"name\":\"张三\",\"date\":\"2024-03-25\",\"amount\":1234.56,\"phone\":\"13800138000\"}"},
    {"id": "tc_002", "input": "李四,2024-3-26,$567.89,13912345678", "expected": "{\"name\":\"李四\",\"date\":\"2024-03-26\",\"amount\":567.89,\"phone\":\"13912345678\"}"},
    {"id": "tc_003", "input": "王五,2024/03/27,€999.99,18612345678", "expected": "{\"name\":\"王五\",\"date\":\"2024-03-27\",\"amount\":999.99,\"phone\":\"18612345678\"}"},
    {"id": "tc_004", "input": "", "expected": "null"},
    {"id": "tc_005", "input": "赵六,2024/03/28,$0,15912345678", "expected": "{\"name\":\"赵六\",\"date\":\"2024-03-28\",\"amount\":0.0,\"phone\":\"15912345678\"}"},
    {"id": "tc_006", "input": "重复行,2024/03/29,¥100,13712345678", "expected": "忽略重复"},
    {"id": "tc_007", "input": "钱七,2024年3月25日,¥888.88,13612345678", "expected": "{\"name\":\"钱七\",\"date\":\"2024-03-25\",\"amount\":888.88,\"phone\":\"13612345678\"}"},
    {"id": "tc_008", "input": "孙八,March 25, 2024,$1500.50,13512345678", "expected": "{\"name\":\"孙八\",\"date\":\"2024-03-25\",\"amount\":1500.50,\"phone\":\"13512345678\"}"}
  ],
  "test_data_file": "dirty_data.csv",
  "toolchain_requirements": ["git_push"]
}
